            <thetext>If a generator config file (e.g. testconfig.json in directory test) contains a statement like 

&quot;library&quot; :
      [
        {                                                                              
          &quot;manifest&quot;     : &quot;libdir/Manifest.json&quot;
        }
      ]

the manifest is not read from (test/libdir), but from the CD the generator is currently running in (generatorCD/libdir).

Relative paths should be relative to the config file they are in.</thetext>
